                <Paragraphs>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>Terms: We'll hereby agree to pay at Manila the total amount of this invoice demand unless otherwise agreed upon. In case of default payments, 24% interest per annum shall be charged on all overdue accounts plus 25% of the amount for attorney's fees and plus cost of collection. The parties expressly submit themselves to the jurisdiction of the court of City of Manila to any legal action arising out of this transaction. We'll further agree that goods described herein will remain exclusive property of Sunshine Multi Plus Corporation until fully paid. Goods travel at the risk of buyer. Seller's responsibilities ceases upon delivery to carrier in good order and conditions.</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontSize>5pt</FontSize>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style>
                      <TextAlign>Left</TextAlign>
